paths: Obvious exits: north, east, south, west
description: The neatness of the crypt is gone and so is the formality shown the dead.  Most bodies are dumped, two and three at a time, into the slots.  The stench of rotting flesh is very heavy and you take in short shallow breaths in hopes of not being overwhelmed by the stench.
title: [Hall of the Dead, Debtors Vault]
